WEBVTT

00:33.970 --> 00:37.220
致敬斯坦·李

02:04.270 --> 02:08.860
<b>哈拉</b>

02:04.520 --> 02:08.860
<b>克里文明首都</b>

02:13.780 --> 02:15.140
你知道现在几点吗
Do you know what time it is?

02:15.490 --> 02:16.570
睡不着
Can't sleep.

02:16.580 --> 02:18.320
有药片治失眠的
There are tabs for that.

02:19.000 --> 02:20.740
没错  但吃了我不就睡着了
Yeah, but then I'd be sleeping.

02:21.270 --> 02:22.500
又做梦了
Dreams again?

02:27.240 --> 02:28.390
想打架吗
Wanna fight?

02:32.550 --> 02:33.150
我滑倒了
I slipped.

02:33.150 --> 02:34.270
是啊  你滑倒了
Right, you slipped

02:34.270 --> 02:36.460
因为我一拳打在了你脸上
as a result of me punching you in the face.

02:36.460 --> 02:37.170
你打到我脸的时候
I was already slipping

02:37.170 --> 02:38.570
我就已经要滑倒了
when you happened to punch me in the face.

02:38.570 --> 02:40.060
这两件事毫不相关
The two events were not related.

02:40.750 --> 02:42.250
跟我说说这个梦
Tell me about this dream.

02:44.520 --> 02:46.280
-有什么新内容吗  -没有
- Anything new? - No.

02:51.210 --> 02:52.710
你必须放下过去
You have to let go of the past.

02:52.710 --> 02:54.000
我不记得我的过去了
I don't remember my past.

02:54.010 --> 02:55.460
这让你产生怀疑
It's causing you doubt,

02:55.650 --> 02:57.590
怀疑让你有弱点
and doubt makes you vulnerable.

03:05.680 --> 03:06.860
控制住
Control it.

03:08.540 --> 03:09.520
如果你再次失控
Lose control again,

03:09.520 --> 03:12.000
就得去找至高智慧密谈了
and you'll have to commune with the Supreme Intelligence.

03:12.000 --> 03:15.080
对于战士而言  情绪是最危险的
There's nothing more dangerous to a warrior than emotion.

03:18.260 --> 03:20.520
幽默使人分心
Humor is a distraction.

03:22.750 --> 03:23.790
而愤怒
And anger?

03:24.040 --> 03:25.790
愤怒只会帮助你的敌人
Anger only serves the enemy.

03:37.090 --> 03:40.240
距最后一次斯库鲁侵袭已过去了120天
One hundred twenty days since the last Skrull attack.

03:40.610 --> 03:41.820
有人见过
Has anyone ever seen

03:41.830 --> 03:43.900
至高智慧的真面目吗
what the Supreme Intelligence really looks like?

03:43.900 --> 03:48.090
没人能看到至高智慧的真面目
No one can look upon the Supreme Intelligence in its true form.

03:48.820 --> 03:49.970
你知道的
You know that.

03:51.210 --> 03:53.700
我们的潜意识会选择我们所能看到的形象
Our subconscious chooses the way they appear to us.

03:53.700 --> 03:55.120
因此它是神圣的
So it's sacred.

03:55.760 --> 03:57.050
也是私密的
It's personal.

03:57.200 --> 03:59.230
克里人绝对不会泄露这个秘密
No Kree divulges it, ever.

03:59.640 --> 04:00.740
你会看到谁
Who do you see?

04:01.370 --> 04:02.520
-你哥哥吗  -不是
- Your brother? - No.

04:02.520 --> 04:03.880
-父亲  -不是
- Father? - No.

04:03.890 --> 04:06.170
-你以前的指挥官  -弗斯
- Your old commander? - Vers.

04:06.170 --> 04:07.810
你看到的是我  对吧
It's me you see, isn't it?

04:08.770 --> 04:10.230
我知道你想干什么
I see what you're trying to do.

04:10.460 --> 04:12.110
-这招有用吗  -有用
- Is it working? - Yes.

04:12.150 --> 04:13.920
但你别想转移话题
But you won't succeed in changing the subject.

04:13.930 --> 04:16.390
如果你不希望我使用这力量
What is the point of giving me these...

04:16.400 --> 04:18.020
那还何必把它给我
if you don't want me to use them?

04:18.130 --> 04:19.410
我希望你使用这力量
I want you to use them.

04:19.980 --> 04:21.700
至高智慧让我负责
The Supreme Intelligence gave me a responsibility...

04:21.700 --> 04:23.950
教会你如何使用这力量
of showing you how to use them.

04:23.950 --> 04:24.900
我知道怎么用
I know how.

04:24.900 --> 04:25.710
如果你真会用
Yeah, if that were true,

04:25.710 --> 04:27.360
就能不用它也可以打倒我了
you'd be able to knock me down without them.

04:28.650 --> 04:30.600
控制你的冲动
Control your impulses.

04:31.900 --> 04:34.360
不要用这儿  而是用这儿
Stop using this, start using this.

04:35.060 --> 04:39.350
我希望你成为最好的自己
I want you to be the best version of yourself.

04:41.510 --> 04:45.600
<b>至高智慧</b>

04:41.760 --> 04:45.600
<b>克里文明的人工智能领袖</b>

05:20.090 --> 05:21.410
弗斯
Vers.

05:22.380 --> 05:23.720
至高智慧
Intelligence.

05:24.220 --> 05:27.320
你的指挥官坚称你已可以服役
Your commander insists that you're fit to serve.

05:27.480 --> 05:28.660
是的
I am.

05:28.830 --> 05:31.870
你在苦苦纠结你的情绪
You struggle with your emotions...

05:32.430 --> 05:34.840
和你的过去  这助长了它们
with your past, which fuels them.

05:36.430 --> 05:39.570
你只是斯库鲁扩张的受害者之一
You are just one victim of the Skrull expansion...

05:39.570 --> 05:42.840
几世纪以来  他们一直威胁着我们的文明
that has threatened our civilization for centuries.

05:42.840 --> 05:45.930
这些卧底暗中潜入
Imposters who silently infiltrate...

05:45.930 --> 05:48.140
然后占领我们的星球
then take over our planets.

05:50.050 --> 05:51.670
你只记得些许可怕之事
Horrors that you remember...

05:51.670 --> 05:54.550
而大部分已忘却
and so much that you do not.

05:58.090 --> 06:01.430
我的人生一片空白
It's all blank. My life.

06:01.950 --> 06:03.020
你的形象应该是
You're supposed to take the form

06:03.020 --> 06:04.780
我最钦佩的人
of who I most admire...

06:04.900 --> 06:09.440
但我甚至都不记得这人是我的什么人了
but I don't even remember who this person was to me.

06:09.630 --> 06:11.230
或许这样也好
Perhaps this is a mercy

06:11.620 --> 06:13.890
让你免受更多痛苦
sparing you from a deeper pain.

06:14.510 --> 06:17.520
让你放开手脚去做所有克里人该做之事
Freeing you to do what all Kree must...

06:18.470 --> 06:20.790
将人民的需求置于自身之上
Put your people's needs before your own.

06:21.170 --> 06:23.380
我们赐予了你伟大的赠礼
We've given you a great gift.

06:23.390 --> 06:26.720
一个为全体克里人而战的机会
The chance to fight for the good of all Kree.

06:27.660 --> 06:28.820
我想要尽忠
I want to serve.

06:28.820 --> 06:30.610
那就学会自控
Then master yourself.

06:30.990 --> 06:33.200
赐予你的也能收回
What was given can be taken away.

06:38.280 --> 06:39.220
我不会让你失望的
I won't let you down.

06:39.220 --> 06:40.930
我们很快就会见分晓了
We'll know soon enough.

06:42.090 --> 06:43.420
你有一项任务
You have a mission.

06:44.790 --> 06:47.310
尽职尽忠  恪守荣耀
Serve well, and with honor.

07:08.130 --> 07:09.710
一定是出大事了
This can't be good.

07:09.770 --> 07:11.690
肯定又是斯库鲁侵袭
Must be another Skrull attack.

07:11.890 --> 07:13.360
反正是大事
Whatever it is, it's big.

07:14.270 --> 07:15.720
有斯库鲁人模仿过你吗
Has a Skrull ever simmed you?

07:15.730 --> 07:16.820
有过一次
Once.

07:16.900 --> 07:18.820
-让我深感不安  -为什么
- It was deeply disturbing. - Why?

07:18.820 --> 07:21.390
因为当我凝视死敌之时
Because I stared into the face of my mortal enemy...

07:21.390 --> 07:23.390
看到的却是我自己
and the face staring back was my own.

07:23.390 --> 07:24.690
也许你要是再帅点
Maybe if you were more attractive,

07:24.690 --> 07:26.540
就不会那么不安了
then it would be less disturbing.

07:26.540 --> 07:28.950
你觉得自己很幽默  可我并不觉得好笑
You think you're funny, but I'm not laughing.

07:28.950 --> 07:29.950
你从来不笑
You never laugh.

07:29.960 --> 07:32.470
我只是笑不外露
I laugh on the inside.

07:33.240 --> 07:34.210
我现在并没笑
I'm not doing that now.

07:34.210 --> 07:35.870
说来好笑  因为客观来讲
It's funny 'cause, objectively speaking,

07:35.880 --> 07:36.880
你还挺帅的
you're quite handsome.

07:36.890 --> 07:37.870
多谢
Well, thank you.

07:37.870 --> 07:39.970
好了  小队  别闹了
Listen up, team. Knock it off.

07:40.870 --> 07:41.850
好
All right.

07:42.290 --> 07:44.240
准备去
Prepare for...

07:45.440 --> 07:48.500
搜救我们的间谍  索拉
a search and rescue of our spy, Soh-Larr.

07:48.500 --> 07:51.340
斯库鲁人又入侵了一个边境星球
The Skrulls have invaded yet another border planet.

07:51.350 --> 07:53.160
这次是托法
This time, Torfa.

07:53.440 --> 07:54.600
索拉发来了警告
Soh-Larr sent us a warning.

07:54.600 --> 07:57.950
但信号遭到了拦截  他的身份也曝光了
The signal was intercepted, and his cover's blown.

08:00.080 --> 08:01.390
斯库鲁将军塔罗斯
The Skrull general, Talos,

08:01.390 --> 08:03.600
派了击杀小队去找他
has sent kill units to find him.

08:03.640 --> 08:05.120
如果他们在我们之前找到他
Should they reach him before we do...

08:05.120 --> 08:07.120
那他这三年来收集的情报
the intelligence he's acquired over three years

08:07.120 --> 08:08.680
就等于送给他们了
is as good as theirs.

08:09.430 --> 08:13.160
指控者将轰炸南部这里的一个斯库鲁要塞
The Accusers will bomb a Skrull stronghold here in the south.

08:13.160 --> 08:16.250
我们潜入  找到索拉
We slip in, we locate Soh-Larr...

08:16.690 --> 08:19.450
然后出来  神不知鬼不觉
and we get out, leaving them none the wiser.

08:19.820 --> 08:21.400
托法人
The Torfan populace.

08:22.070 --> 08:23.420
我们不要干扰他们
We are not to interfere with them,

08:23.420 --> 08:24.270
也不要被他们缠住
nor them with us.

08:24.270 --> 08:28.200
我们任务的机密性是第一位的
Nothing compromises the security of our mission.

08:28.210 --> 08:29.940
务必万分小心
Proceed with caution.

08:30.050 --> 08:32.430
撤离他前遵循规程
Follow protocol before extracting him.

08:34.070 --> 08:35.690
此次任务很危险
This is a dangerous mission.

08:35.840 --> 08:38.110
我们要做好加入大集体的准备
We must all be ready to join the Collective

08:38.470 --> 08:40.160
若那是我们今日的命数
if that is our fate today.

08:40.240 --> 08:41.460
为全体克里人而战
For the good of all Kree.

08:41.460 --> 08:43.120
为全体克里人而战
For the good of all Kree!

08:57.310 --> 09:01.180
<b>托法</b>

08:57.560 --> 09:01.180
<b>克里边境星球</b>

09:52.680 --> 09:54.670
弗斯  追踪索拉的信标
Vers, track Soh-Larr's beacon.

09:55.400 --> 09:57.700
阿特拉斯  米涅瓦  找到高地
Att-Lass, Minn-Erva, find elevation.

10:16.890 --> 10:18.550
外围有本地人
Locals on the periphery.

10:19.540 --> 10:20.600
可能有十几个
Maybe a dozen.

10:20.960 --> 10:21.960
米涅瓦
Minn-Erva?

10:23.620 --> 10:26.430
收到吗  有人收到吗
Do you read me? Does anybody copy?

10:27.500 --> 10:28.530
重复
Repeat.

10:41.410 --> 10:43.790
他的信标信号在那个寺庙里  我们走
His beacon's coming from that temple. Let's move.

10:43.790 --> 10:46.610
不  这里太适合伏击了
No. This is a perfect spot for an ambush.

10:46.810 --> 10:48.300
只有一条路进出
Only one way in, only one way out.

10:48.300 --> 10:49.650
我们可以绕过本地人
We can get past the locals.

10:49.650 --> 10:51.280
我们都不能确定他们是否真是本地人
We don't know if they are locals.

10:51.810 --> 10:52.470
太冒险
Too risky.

10:52.470 --> 10:53.640
你不用跟我一起去  我可以自己去
You don't have to go with me. I'll go alone.

10:53.640 --> 10:55.030
不  不行
No, you won't.

10:59.820 --> 11:01.940
好吧  我们不要走远
Right. We keep a close radius.

11:01.990 --> 11:04.000
如果断联  就回氦核飞船碰头
We lose comms, we meet back at the Helion.

11:05.040 --> 11:06.010
走吧
Come on.

11:18.600 --> 11:19.970
阿特拉斯  你看到了吗
Att-Lass, you getting this?

11:19.970 --> 11:21.410
收到  看到了
Copy. I see them.

11:31.640 --> 11:32.640
退后
Get back!

11:33.470 --> 11:34.540
指挥官
Commander?

11:42.050 --> 11:44.030
退后  退后
Get back! Back!

11:45.000 --> 11:47.230
米涅瓦  你看到了吗
Minn-Erva? Do you have eyes on this?

11:48.990 --> 11:50.600
拦住他们  米涅瓦
Keep them back. Minn-Erva?

11:50.970 --> 11:52.110
有人收到吗
Does anybody copy?

11:56.850 --> 11:58.340
我不想伤害你
I don't wanna hurt you.

12:00.920 --> 12:02.040
别过来
Keep back!

12:05.360 --> 12:06.440
别过来
Stay back!

12:10.620 --> 12:13.400
他们是本地人  我发现两具尸体  没有绿血
They're locals. I found two dead. No green.

12:13.420 --> 12:14.740
他们只是饿了
They're just starving.

12:40.250 --> 12:42.010
HGX78
Hgx-78.

12:42.030 --> 12:44.970
TRT79  VVX6
Trt79-vvx6.

12:47.880 --> 12:49.030
退后
Get back.

12:57.500 --> 12:59.310
斯库鲁人
Skrulls!

13:16.540 --> 13:17.680
弗斯
Vers!

13:17.680 --> 13:19.890
弗斯  斯库鲁人
Vers? Skrulls.

13:20.050 --> 13:21.260
是埋伏
It's an ambush.

13:40.400 --> 13:41.520
敌舰
Incoming!

13:47.110 --> 13:48.380
回氦核飞船去
Back to the Helion.

13:48.660 --> 13:50.360
弗斯  收到吗
Vers. Do you copy?

13:51.120 --> 13:52.270
回氦核飞船去
Back to the Helion.

13:52.680 --> 13:53.650
回复  弗斯
Come in. Vers.

13:53.660 --> 13:56.110
你怎么会知道密码
How did you know the code?

13:56.300 --> 13:58.660
我可以告诉你我的秘密
How about I tell you my secret...

14:00.210 --> 14:02.130
但你先说你的
when you've told me yours?

14:06.090 --> 14:07.760
敞开她吧
Let's open her up.

14:19.810 --> 14:21.980
我们在哪
Where are we?

14:21.980 --> 14:23.140
就绪
Stand by.

14:25.540 --> 14:26.700
你想什么呢[脑袋在哪]
Where's your head at?

14:27.630 --> 14:29.940
想云彩[胡思乱想]  你呢
In the clouds. Where's yours?

14:29.970 --> 14:31.350
在我肩膀上
On my shoulders.

14:31.400 --> 14:33.390
要让这些男的见识一下我们的本事
About to show these boys how we do it.

14:33.390 --> 14:34.380
你准备好了吗
You ready?

14:35.100 --> 14:36.540
更高  更远  更快啊  亲爱的
Higher, further, faster, baby.

14:36.540 --> 14:37.710
没错
That's right.

14:46.570 --> 14:48.100
这不对
This can't be right.

14:49.870 --> 14:51.220
再往前倒
Go back even further.

14:55.560 --> 14:58.490
你开太快了  你得慢点
You're going too fast! You need to go slow!

15:11.690 --> 15:14.230
这人是谁  我们找对...
Who is this person? Are we in the right...?

15:14.230 --> 15:15.590
你怎么想的
What the hell are you thinking?

15:15.600 --> 15:16.540
你不该来这里
You don't belong out here!

15:16.540 --> 15:18.100
我们好像倒得太多了
I think we went back too far.

15:18.230 --> 15:19.550
你让他开了
You let him drive.

15:19.550 --> 15:20.930
我试试吧
Let me try something.

15:23.610 --> 15:24.820
放弃吧
Give up already!

15:25.310 --> 15:26.690
你不该来这里
You don't belong out here!

15:29.450 --> 15:31.110
你不够强壮
You're not strong enough.

15:31.240 --> 15:32.780
你会害死自己的
You'll kill yourself.

15:38.630 --> 15:39.780
他们绝不会让你飞的
They'll never let you fly.

15:39.780 --> 15:42.820
只有我一个人看糊涂了吗
Am I the only one that's confused here?

15:42.830 --> 15:44.410
你是个好飞行员
You're a decent pilot.

15:44.740 --> 15:46.090
但你太情绪化
But you're too emotional.

15:46.090 --> 15:49.160
你知道那为什么叫驾驶舱[屌坑]吧
You do know why they call it a cockpit, don't you?

15:56.500 --> 15:59.490
一声贯穿宇宙的巨响  震动了月亮
A huge rumble throughout the cosmos shook the moon...

15:59.740 --> 16:01.880
太阳  和天上的星星
and the sun and the stars in the sky.

16:02.760 --> 16:03.590
于是
And so,

16:03.590 --> 16:06.070
小阿露蒂整夜飞上天空
little Alouette flew up throughout the night.

16:06.070 --> 16:08.650
你看到她了吗  那是小阿露蒂
Did you see her? It's Alouette.

16:10.040 --> 16:12.010
给我进来  该吃饭了
Get your butts inside, it's time to eat.

16:12.020 --> 16:14.460
准备起飞  捣蛋中尉
Prepare for takeoff, Lieutenant Trouble.

16:14.460 --> 16:15.820
有趣的记忆
Charming memory.

16:15.820 --> 16:16.980
等等
Hang on.

16:17.360 --> 16:18.710
我好像找到了
I think I've got it.

16:23.130 --> 16:24.550
咕咕喜欢你
Goose likes you.

16:24.740 --> 16:26.210
她一般不怎么亲近人的
She doesn't typically take to people.

16:26.210 --> 16:27.660
你起得好早
Early start to your morning.

16:27.700 --> 16:28.880
其实是晚上熬夜了
Late night, actually.

16:28.890 --> 16:30.840
还有工作  我就睡不着
I can't sleep when there's work to do.

16:30.840 --> 16:31.900
耳熟吗
Sound familiar?

16:31.900 --> 16:34.080
我从不觉得飞行是工作
Flying your planes never feels like work.

16:35.530 --> 16:36.830
风景很棒  是吧
Wonderful view, isn't it?

16:36.830 --> 16:38.620
我更喜欢上面的风景
I prefer the view from up there.

16:38.650 --> 16:40.090
你很快就能上去了  王牌
You'll get there soon enough, Ace.

16:40.090 --> 16:42.450
等等  就是她  倒回去
Wait! Wait, wait! That's her. Get her back.

16:42.450 --> 16:43.550
就绪
Stand by.

16:47.640 --> 16:48.960
耳熟吗
Sound familiar?

16:49.200 --> 16:50.860
风景很棒  是吧
Wonderful view, isn't it?

16:52.930 --> 16:54.590
我更喜欢上面的风景
I prefer the view from up there.

16:54.590 --> 16:55.760
你很快就能上去了  王牌
You'll get there soon enough, Ace.

16:55.760 --> 16:56.830
她衣服上写着什么
What's that on her shirt?

16:56.830 --> 16:58.200
