Go back right before this. Go back.

17:39.360 --> 17:40.440
那可不是米格  劳森
That's no MiG, Lawson.

17:40.440 --> 17:42.750
就是这个  让我看看你要去哪
This is it. Now let me see where you're headed.

17:43.480 --> 17:45.430
没错  看看坐标
