17:52.630 --> 17:53.710
快看到了
You're almost there.

17:53.710 --> 17:55.810
快看到了  别抵抗
You're almost there. Don't fight it.

17:57.490 --> 17:58.640
集中精神
Focus!

18:00.480 --> 18:02.790
把她拉回来  快点
Get her back! Get her back now!

18:06.700 --> 18:08.450
这没道理
This doesn't make any sense.

18:22.600 --> 18:26.880
我们拿到任何可以行动的情报了吗
Do we have any information we can act on?

18:26.880 --> 18:29.970
只知道劳森在C53星球上某处
Just that Lawson was somewhere on planet C-53.

18:30.320 --> 18:31.250
我们这就去
We're on our way.

18:31.250 --> 18:33.570
那就再继续深挖
Then dig, dig, dig deeper.

18:34.040 --> 18:37.060
劳森能带我们找到光速引擎
Lawson is our link to that light-speed engine!

18:38.710 --> 18:40.550
和我们想要的一切
And everything we're after.

18:49.660 --> 18:50.910
刚刚那下有用
