19:27.930 --> 19:30.670
怪不得你稀里糊涂的
I'm not surprised you can't keep it straight.

19:30.680 --> 19:32.510
他们真把你祸害得不轻
They really did a number on you.

19:32.680 --> 19:33.760
少跟我玩心理战
Enough of your mind games.

19:33.760 --> 19:35.570
你想要什么
What do you want?

19:37.320 --> 19:39.980
我们在找一位劳森博士
We're looking for the location of a Dr. Lawson...

19:39.980 --> 19:41.700
和她的光速引擎
and her light-speed engine.

19:41.700 --> 19:43.360
我不认识什么劳森博士
I don't know any Dr. Lawson.

19:43.370 --> 19:46.720
是吗  那她为什么在你脑袋里
Really? Then why is she in your head?

20:18.120 --> 20:18.950
你们不会刚好知道
You guys wouldn't happen to know

20:18.950 --> 20:20.670
这玩意怎么拿下来吧
how these things come off, would ya?

20:21.050 --> 20:21.960
不吗
No?

20:21.960 --> 20:22.930
好吧
Fine.

22:01.220 --> 22:03.050
你知道那为什么叫...
You do know why they call it a...

22:20.770 --> 22:22.280
这就走了
You leaving so soon?

22:23.010 --> 22:24.900
我们才刚认识
We're just getting to know each other.

