Yeah. I understand you.

24:36.050 --> 24:37.130
好的
Oh, good.

24:37.200 --> 24:39.300
你负责这一带的安全吗
Are you in charge of security for this district?

24:40.800 --> 24:43.900
算是吧  影院有自己的保安
Sort of. Uh, the movie theater has its own guy.

24:45.230 --> 24:47.610
我去哪能找到通讯设备
Where can I find communications equipment?

24:52.090 --> 24:53.760
<b>睿侠</b>

24:54.260 --> 24:55.290
谢谢
Thank you.

25:28.320 --> 25:30.210
追踪飞行舱  找到那姑娘
Track the pod. Find the girl.

25:31.500 --> 25:33.750
她知道的情报比自己以为的多
She knows more than she knows.

25:38.500 --> 25:39.950
这个我要了
This one's taken.

25:50.810 --> 25:51.870
拜托
Come on.

25:52.580 --> 25:53.650
弗斯
Vers?

25:53.700 --> 25:54.720
弗斯
Vers?

25:55.530 --> 25:57.430
证实身份  CTC39
Verify. CTC-39.

25:57.440 --> 25:58.990
GRXV1600
Grxv-1600.

25:58.990 --> 26:00.750
我很好  多谢关心
And I'm fine, thank you for asking.

26:01.000 --> 26:02.430
大家还好吗  发生了什么
Is everyone okay? What happened?

26:02.430 --> 26:04.170
斯库鲁伏击
Skrull ambush.

26:04.580 --> 26:06.000
我以为我们失去你了
I thought we'd lost you.

26:06.310 --> 26:07.310
你找到索拉了吗
Did you find Soh-Larr?

26:07.310 --> 26:08.620
那根本不是索拉
It wasn't Soh-Larr.

26:08.620 --> 26:11.100
是塔罗斯模仿了他  连他的密码都知道
Talos simmed him. Even knew his code.

26:11.360 --> 26:12.540
那不可能
That's impossible.

26:13.370 --> 26:15.350
那密码是在他的潜意识里的
That code was buried in his unconscious.

26:15.350 --> 26:16.710
斯库鲁人动了我的大脑
The Skrulls messed with my mind.

26:16.710 --> 26:17.570
他们用的那台机器
The machine that they used...

26:17.570 --> 26:20.400
我觉得他们就是那样得知了索拉的密码
I think it's how they extracted Soh-Larr's code.

26:20.410 --> 26:21.470
弗斯  你在哪
Vers, where are you?

26:21.470 --> 26:23.210
我在C53星球上
I'm on planet C-53.

26:23.670 --> 26:25.800
斯库鲁在找一个叫劳森的人
The Skrulls are looking for someone named Lawson.

26:26.330 --> 26:27.370
谁
Who?

26:27.780 --> 26:30.890
她是我看到的人
She's who I see.

26:31.060 --> 26:32.140
她什么
She's what?

26:33.400 --> 26:34.400
弗斯
Vers?

26:35.790 --> 26:37.080
弗斯  什么
Vers, what?

26:38.210 --> 26:39.610
她是个科学家
She's a scientist.

26:39.610 --> 26:41.600
他们觉得她研发出了光速科技
They think that she's cracked the code on light-speed tech.

26:41.600 --> 26:42.880
我得赶在他们之前找到她
I have to get to her before they do...

26:42.880 --> 26:44.910
否则他们就能入侵新星系了
or else they'll be able to invade new galaxies.

26:44.910 --> 26:47.290
不  你已经被抓到一次了
No. You've been caught once already.

26:47.970 --> 26:49.630
C53离我们多远
How far is C-53?

26:50.100 --> 26:52.520
离最近的跳跃点有22小时的路程
Closest jump point is 22 hours.

26:52.770 --> 26:54.980
弗斯  原地别动  等我们赶到
Vers, hold your position until we get there.

26:54.980 --> 26:57.110
保持通讯器在线  以便我们联系你
Keep your comms online so we can contact you.

26:57.110 --> 26:59.010
不  如果他们先于我找到...
No! What if they get a hold of it before...

26:59.020 --> 27:00.030
很抱歉
We're sorry.

27:00.030 --> 27:02.130
您拨打的号码需要输入
A long-distance company access code

27:02.130 --> 27:03.400
-长途电话公司  -勇
- is required for the number - Yon?

27:03.400 --> 27:04.960
-接入码  -弗斯
- you have dialed. - Vers?

27:04.960 --> 27:06.270
-弗斯  -请用接入码
- Vers? - Please dial your call

27:06.270 --> 27:07.890
拨打电话
with the access code.

27:07.890 --> 27:08.980
弗斯
Vers?

27:10.050 --> 27:11.390
如果斯库鲁人控制了她的心智
If the Skrulls got to her,

27:11.390 --> 27:12.900
她就不能被信任了
she's compromised.

27:12.900 --> 27:14.670
她比你想的要坚强
She's stronger than you think.

27:15.800 --> 27:17.520
去过C53吗
Ever been to C-53?

27:18.420 --> 27:19.420
去过一次
Once.

27:20.460 --> 27:22.170
破地方
It's a real shithole.

27:33.060 --> 27:35.230
新人  去跟那个保安谈谈
Rookie! Go talk to the rent-a-cop.

27:42.910 --> 27:44.040
是你上报的吗
Did you call this in?

27:59.260 --> 28:01.070
信标激活
Beacon activated.

28:03.460 --> 28:04.670
打扰  小姐
Excuse me, miss.

28:04.960 --> 28:07.430
你知道有位女士把那边的
You know anything about a lady blowing a hole

28:07.440 --> 28:10.150
百视达屋顶轰了个洞吗
through the roof of that Blockbuster over there?

28:10.500 --> 28:13.450
证人说她穿了一身激光枪战的衣服
Witness says she was dressed for laser tag.

28:16.470 --> 28:18.140
嗯  我觉得她去那边了
Yeah, I think she went that way.

28:19.620 --> 28:21.900
我想问你些问题
I'd like to ask you some questions.

28:22.510 --> 28:26.290
或许教教你怎么用深夜投件箱
Maybe give you the 411 on the late-night drop box.

28:26.740 --> 28:28.660
可以出示身份证吗
Could I see some identification, please?

28:28.860 --> 28:30.480
弗斯  克里星际战队
Vers. Kree Starforce.

28:30.480 --> 28:32.770
我们不把身份证明写在小纸片上
We don't carry our identification on little cards.

28:32.770 --> 28:33.880
弗斯
Vers?

28:34.250 --> 28:36.310
星际战队
Starforce?

28:37.710 --> 28:39.070
你打算在这里待多久
How long you plan to be in town?

28:39.070 --> 28:40.340
等我找到
I'll be out of your hair...

28:40.350 --> 28:41.520
正在潜入你们星球的斯库鲁人
as soon as I track down the Skrulls

28:41.530 --> 28:43.470
我就会离开了
that are infiltrating your planet.

28:44.380 --> 28:45.750
斯库鲁人
Skrulls?

28:46.310 --> 28:47.560
变形者
Shapeshifters?

28:47.560 --> 28:50.610
他们能变形成任何生命形式  连DNA也能复制
They can transform into any life-form down to the DNA.

28:51.990 --> 28:54.300
天呐  你们完全不知道  是吧
Oh, boy. You guys don't have any clue, do you?

28:54.810 --> 28:55.880
等等
Hold on.

28:57.090 --> 29:02.580
我们怎么知道你不是那种变形者
How do we know you're not one of those shapeshifters?

29:02.620 --> 29:04.340
恭喜  弗瑞特工
Congratulations, Agent Fury.

29:04.340 --> 29:06.290
你总算问了个有用的问题
You have finally asked a relevant question.

29:06.290 --> 29:09.380
不  恭喜你  星际战队女士
No! Congratulations to you, Starforce lady.

29:09.380 --> 29:11.090
你被捕了
You're under arrest.

29:19.620 --> 29:20.610
新人
Rook!

29:21.600 --> 29:22.930
新人  我们走
Rook, let's roll!

29:32.600 --> 29:33.930
你看到她的武器了吗
Did you see her weapon?

29:33.930 --> 29:34.950
没有
I did not.

29:44.800 --> 29:45.880
看路啊
Watch it!

30:18.700 --> 30:21.610
嫌疑人在北行列车上  正在追赶
Suspect on northbound train. In pursuit.

30:42.150 --> 30:45.240
"相信我  真正的信徒"  "相信我"
"Trust me, true believer." "Trust me."

30:42.600 --> 30:43.780
<b>耍酷一族</b>

30:49.870 --> 30:51.820
"相信我  真正的信徒"
"Trust me, true believer."

31:37.920 --> 31:39.110
放开
Get off!

32:35.130 --> 32:37.040
列车前面要进隧道了
Train's heading for a tunnel up ahead.

32:39.680 --> 32:41.700
我们去车站接他们
Let's greet them at the station.

32:53.370 --> 32:55.460
弗瑞先生  这里是科尔森特工
Mr. Fury, this is Agent Coulson.

32:56.090 --> 32:59.160
我还在百视达呢
I'm still here at the Blockbuster. And, uh,

33:00.490 --> 33:01.710
大家都哪去了
where'd everybody go?

33:02.250 --> 33:03.950
我已经完成证据收集了
I finished collecting evidence...

34:32.580 --> 34:33.720
快叫救护车
We need an ambulance!

34:33.840 --> 34:35.470
谁打下911
Someone call 911!

34:39.950 --> 34:42.800
神盾局官方行动  别过来
Official S.H.I.E.L.D. activity. Stay back.

34:55.030 --> 34:56.610
<b>温迪·劳森博士  飞马计划</b>

34:58.450 --> 35:00.950
<b>潘乔酒吧</b>

