<b>该设备已断网或被占用</b>

35:31.670 --> 35:33.290
潜水衣挺酷
Nice scuba suit.

35:38.740 --> 35:40.120
幽默点嘛  亲爱的
Lighten up, honey, huh?

35:40.800 --> 35:42.160
能给我笑笑吗
Got a smile for me?

35:47.240 --> 35:48.300
怪胎
Freak.

36:07.370 --> 36:10.790
所有地球上的生命都是碳基的  但他不是
All life on Earth is carbon-based. Not this guy.

36:11.160 --> 36:12.610
不管他是什么做的
Whatever he runs on,

36:13.450 --> 36:15.110
反正周期表上没有
it's not on the periodic table.

36:15.180 --> 36:17.770
你是说  他不是这里的
You're saying he's not from around here?

36:18.930 --> 36:20.200
你的眼睛怎么样了
How's your eye?

36:20.800 --> 36:22.920
眼睛倒没事
Well, I'd say fine...

36:23.310 --> 36:25.650
就是不敢相信我看到的东西
but it can't believe what it's seeing.

36:28.250 --> 36:33.600
你说这玩意之前是科尔森的样子
You say this thing looked like Coulson?

36:33.820 --> 36:35.100
说话也像
Talked like him, too.

36:35.540 --> 36:38.180
那女人说还有更多这种人
And the woman said that there were more?

36:38.180 --> 36:40.480
她说的是"潜入"
The word she used was "infiltration."

36:40.490 --> 36:41.580
你相信她吗
You believe her?

36:41.610 --> 36:43.280
直到见到这个才信
Not till I saw this.

36:44.980 --> 36:46.340
你有什么打算
What's your plan?

36:47.110 --> 36:48.980
我能找到那个百视达姑娘
I'll find Blockbuster girl.

36:48.980 --> 36:50.940
有桩摩托车盗窃的报案
I got word on a motorcycle thief

36:50.940 --> 36:52.550
女贼符合她的描述
that fits her description.

36:53.250 --> 36:55.460
如果她能说出这些蜥蜴人为什么来
If she can tell us why these lizards are here...

36:56.070 --> 36:58.550
或许她也能告诉我们怎么赶走他们
maybe she can tell us how to kick 'em to the curb.

36:58.550 --> 36:59.560
好
Good.

37:00.860 --> 37:03.940
但你自己行动  我们谁都不能信任
Do it alone, though. We can't trust anyone.

37:04.350 --> 37:06.200
连我们自己人都不行
Not even our own men.

37:06.690 --> 37:07.690
是  长官
Yes, sir.

37:23.080 --> 37:25.050
他们可真丑  是吧
They're ugly bastards, aren't they?

37:26.370 --> 37:28.710
是啊  可不比布拉德·皮特  长官
Yeah, well, he's no Brad Pitt, sir.

37:33.770 --> 37:36.160
安然超度吧  我的朋友
Safe journey to the beyond, my friend.

37:38.060 --> 37:41.130
我会完成我们的大业
I will finish what we started.

37:49.600 --> 37:51.230
最好别靠太近  老大
I wouldn't get too close there, boss.

37:53.580 --> 37:55.120
任何人不得进出
No one in or out.

38:57.680 --> 38:58.880
需要点什么
What can I get ya?

38:59.070 --> 39:00.690
这张照片是哪拍的
Where was this photograph taken?

39:01.480 --> 39:02.700
一个机场
An airport.

39:02.700 --> 39:03.990
飞马计划在哪
Where's Pegasus?

39:04.000 --> 39:05.860
那是机密
That's classified.

39:06.120 --> 39:09.100
我给你建立的档案也是
Not unlike the file I started on you.

39:11.510 --> 39:13.950
但看来你还换装了
But I see you've changed it up a bit since then.

39:14.070 --> 39:15.530
垃圾摇滚挺衬你
Grunge is a good look for you.

39:15.530 --> 39:17.250
你今天不顺吗  弗瑞特工
Did you have a rough day, Agent Fury?

39:17.250 --> 39:18.990
还行吧
It was cool, you know?

39:19.000 --> 39:21.870
遭遇了太空入侵  大型追车
Had a space invasion, big car chase.

39:21.870 --> 39:25.110
