Got to watch an alien autopsy.

39:25.880 --> 39:27.260
也就典型的工作日
Typical nine-to-five.

39:27.260 --> 39:28.450
你看到一个了
So you saw one?

39:28.460 --> 39:31.290
我并不怎么信外星人
I was never one to believe in aliens...

39:32.400 --> 39:34.290
但那画面我是忘不掉了
but I can't unsee that.

39:34.750 --> 39:37.410
这会比较尴尬  但我必须问
This is gonna get a little awkward, but I gotta ask.

39:37.410 --> 39:39.740
你觉得我也是那种绿玩意
You think I'm one of those green things.

39:39.860 --> 39:41.070
小心驶得万年船
Can't be too careful.

39:41.070 --> 39:46.160
我可是百分百的红血地球人
You are looking at 100% red-blooded Earth man.

39:46.160 --> 39:47.630
